<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="/">홈</a>
            <a href="/posts">게시글</a>
            <a href="/about">소개</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="hero">
            <h2>환영합니다!</h2>
            <p>기술과 개발에 대한 이야기를 나누는 공간입니다.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="recent-posts">
            <h3>최근 게시글</h3>
            <% if (posts && posts.length > 0) { %>
                <% posts.forEach(post => { %>
                    <article class="post-preview">
                        <h4><a href="/posts/<%= post.id %>"><%= post.title %></a></h4>
                        <p class="post-date"><%= post.date %></p>
                        <p><%= post.excerpt %></p>
                    </article>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <p>아직 게시글이 없습니다.</p>
            <% } %>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 기술 블로그. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>